### Description of Issue/Question
When service messagebus is stopped on a rhel based system we get the error that salt can not connect to dbus
### Setup
(Please provide relevant configs and/or SLS files (Be sure to remove sensitive info).)
[ERROR   ] org.freedesktop.DBus.Error.NoServer: Failed to connect to socket /var/run/dbus/system_bus_socket: Connection refused
### Steps to Reproduce Issue
(Include debug logs if possible and relevant.)
service messagebus stop and run any salt state
### Versions Report
(Provided by running `salt --versions-report`. Please also mention any differences in master/minion versions.)
salt 2016.11.2-1.el6
